%F A395266 a(n) = (5*F(n/2) + F((n/2)-1))^2 if n is even and (5*F((n-1)/2) + F(((n-1)/2)-1))*(5*F(((n-1)/2)+1) + F((n-1)/2)) if n is odd where F(n) = Fibonacci(n).
%F A395266 G.f.: (1 + 4*x + 20*x^2 + 4*x^3)/((1 + x^2)*(1 - x - x^2)). - _Stefano Spezia_, Apr 09 2026
